name: Hungry Chaos
description: A dozen kaleidoscopes on atop the other, switching from colors to lineart to interpolated colors, cutting and pasting parts of one variant onto the other... Let's just say that even with 5 intermediate steps saved to disk, I have no idea how exactly this one came to be. I guess that's what happens when you pour a bit of stress and distraction together over several hours dispersed over a week.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
